Title: 构造类型
Describe: None
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
用 `<<` 和 `>>` 来定义角色或者用例的构造类型。

[UML]
@startuml
User << Human >>
:Main Database: as MySql << Application >>
(Start) << One Shot >>
(Use the application) as (Use) << Main >>

User -> (Start)
User --> (Use)

MySql --> (Use)

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
